1
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:09,510
Sorry to keep you waiting.

2
00:00:09,510 --> 00:00:11,490
Let's head back.

3
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:13,010
Oh, okay.

4
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,020
But I wanted to go back with Yuki.

5
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:16,730
Have you seen him?

6
00:00:16,930 --> 00:00:18,560
Morimoto...

7
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:21,700
He looks pretty busy.
Let's just head home for today.

8
00:00:22,270 --> 00:00:24,020
I see.

9
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:26,190
You'll see him next time.

10
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:28,450
You're right.

11
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:34,160
This is a crucial time for him.

12
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:36,700
If word gets out about you two...

13
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:38,660
he might lose everything.

14
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:41,720
Thank you for your hard work! Thank you so much!

15
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:43,760
I'm heading out now.

16
00:00:46,210 --> 00:00:47,760
Goodbye.

17
00:00:50,180 --> 00:00:51,630
Thank you.

18
00:00:51,630 --> 00:00:53,220
Goodbye.

19
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:56,510
You did amazing!

20
00:00:56,510 --> 00:00:58,140
Not at all.
Thank you so much for today...

21
00:00:58,140 --> 00:00:59,600
No, you were really great today!

22
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:04,650
For Makoto's dream...
